author: woonsan
msg: JS2-961: Implements head merging feature in the desktop client-side script (core.src.js).
Removes the unused PortletHeaderRequestImpl and PortletHeaderResponseImpl.
- We do not use Head Aggregation Valve in portal pipeline any more.
- By the way, under desktop pipeline, head contributions are being done by client-side javascript (core.src.js), not by server-side aggregator component.)
Adds merge hint key in HeaderResourceImpl and JPT because the merge hint key should be used by client side javascript to merge some head content.
Marks deprecated on HeaderResource, PortletHeaderRequest, PortletHeaderResponse and SupportsHeaderPhase interface.
